Windows Server Installation in VMware Workstation
Requirement

VMware Workstation (Installed)

Windows Server ISO file (2016 / 2019 / 2022)

Minimum System:

RAM: 4 GB (Recommended 8 GB)

CPU: 2 Cores

Disk: 60 GB

Step 1: Open VMware Workstation

Launch VMware Workstation

Click Create a New Virtual Machine

Step 2: Select Virtual Machine Configuration

Choose Typical (Recommended)

Click Next

Step 3: Select Installation Media

Select Installer disc image file (ISO)

Click Browse

Select Windows Server ISO file

Click Next

Step 4: Select Guest Operating System

Guest OS: Microsoft Windows

Version: Windows Server

Click Next

Step 5: Name Virtual Machine

Enter Virtual Machine Name
Example: Windows_Server_2022

Select Location to store VM

Click Next

Step 6: Specify Disk Capacity

Enter Disk Size: 60 GB

Select Store virtual disk as a single file

Click Next

Step 7: Customize Hardware

Click Customize Hardware

Set:

Memory: 4 GB or more

Processors: 2

Network Adapter: NAT

Click Close

Click Finish

Step 8: Power On Virtual Machine

Click Power on this virtual machine

Windows Server Setup will start

Step 9: Windows Server Setup

Select:

Language

Time and Currency Format

Keyboard Layout

Click Next

Click Install Now

Step 10: Select Windows Server Edition

Choose:

Windows Server Standard (Desktop Experience)

Click Next

Step 11: Accept License Agreement

Check I accept the license terms

Click Next

Step 12: Select Installation Type

Choose Custom: Install Windows only (Advanced)

Step 13: Disk Partition

Select Unallocated Space

Click Next

Windows installation will begin

Step 14: Installation Process

System will copy files

System will restart automatically

Step 15: Administrator Password Setup

Enter Administrator Password

Confirm Password

Click Finish

Step 16: Login to Windows Server

Press Ctrl + Alt + Insert

Login as Administrator

Enter Password

Step 17: Install VMware Tools

Click VM â†’ Install VMware Tools

Open This PC

Run VMware Tools Setup

Complete installation

Restart the Server
